# This is the PUBLIC release-shell repo for Naqi. No source code ships here —
# only README, CHANGELOG, legal, user-facing docs, and GitHub Releases.
# Actual development happens in yasserstudio/naqi-private. See INTERNAL.md in
# that repo for the full split.

# macOS / IDE noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
